  "description": "The CQL Group Definition profile defines conformance expectations for the use of a FHIR Group resource as a cohort definition using Clinical Quality Language (CQL) to define membership criteria. This profile is intended to be consistent with and able to be used as a cohort definition in other similar efforts including clinical trial eligibility in the Evidence-based Medicine on FHIR space, as well as the Bulk Cohort API cohort definition profile.",
